  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">NBD SME Frontier</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">IFC and NBD Bank (the Company) shall realize a 1 billion Russian ruble program of expanding SME finance in frontier regions of the Central part of Russia (NBD SME Frontier or the Project). The proposed IFCs investment consists of a senior local currency loan of up to 500 million Russian rubles (approximately up to $17 million equivalent) up to 5 years to finance SMEs in frontier regions of the Central part of Russia. NBD shall match IFC funding by investing additional 500 million Russian rubles (approximately up to $17 million equivalent) from its own sources.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Project is expected to have a high developmental impact on account of (a) providing access to finance to the Russian SME sector; (b) contribute to new employment generation in small towns of the Central part of Russia.</narrative>
  </description>
